# Code as Anything

Open-source **Code-as-X** router — compose polyglot tool chains from `.work`
sessions.

## Layout

- `cli/` — nexus worktop (catalog, router, API, sessions, UI)
- `tools/` — host runners (`run.sh`, `steps/`, hardware, models, render)
- `skill/` — agent skill (`skill/SKILL.md`) packaged with the project
- `wrappers/` — one `.work` file per maintained tool (`category-tool.work`)
- `eval/` — blind agent scenarios + rubrics
- `Justfile` — portable CLI (project-only install)

## Polyglot rule

The spine is `.work` + `oota new` / `oota run`. Native toolchains
run **locally on the host** via `tools/steps/`.

